<br>
 As far as Willus goes, he is one of the New Combine Empire's Generals. If you have a problem with him then thats not something I can do for you. <br>
<br>
As far as killing your prince?  He attacked me in my own city and the guards did not like his little plan to bring a group of Vah into the city flying a banner of truce and then trying to corrupt a meeting with the presence of a small army in the Council room. You were only to bring your prince and two ambassadors. Not an entire legion. Your distrust got the better of you. Your ears were closed to begin with. Next time your invited to a party, don't bring your entire litter.<br>
