<br>
Emperor is a hefty title indeed.  But tread lightly.  You speak of fighting Hate, Fear, Death and War, but you yourself use these to your own ends.<br>
<br>
You show immense hatred for those who follow the &quot;dark paths,&quot; and yet you wish to fight it.<br>
<br>
You try to drum up support of this bastard Empire by instilling fear in the hearts of those whom you would govern.<br>
<br>
And your very words are a declaration of war against the dark paths, and war leads to death....always.<br>
<br>
Your hypocricy is astounding, Gavin Steelheart.  Call me neutral if you will.  Good, evil, neutral--mere labels we use for convenience.  I am what I am--a student and a teacher.  A leader and a follower.<br>
<br>
I now live, but I will die.  I am peaceful, but will wage war when needed.  I show love to my friends, but hate to my enemies.  Does this make me evil?  Or does it make me a coward?  Talk to those who know me.  You will find I am neither.<br>
<br>
No...I do not recognize this Empire.  And that is for the simple reason that I submit to no one.<br>
<br>
